• Successfully mediated a complex contract dispute, helping both parties avoid a lengthy court battle.  
• Completed a strategic analysis for an intellectual-property case, strengthening your client’s defense ahead of upcoming proceedings.  
• Spent time reflecting on professional growth and work–life balance, gearing up for the next wave of challenges.

Feel free to drop these bullet points straight into your email to Alex or tweak as you like!
